# Optional: enables "Sign in with Google" Drive sync.
# Without this, the app still works fully offline using on-device storage.
#
# Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (type: Web application) in Google Cloud Console,
# add your origins (e.g. http://localhost:5173 and https://<user>.github.io)
# as Authorized JavaScript origins, then paste the client ID here:
#
# Copy this file to ".env" (or ".env.local") and fill in the value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
